reviewText: Too bad there is nothing lower than a 1 to rate this.  Poorly shot, poorly produced, no logical sequence, no historical significance.  Absolutely the greatest waste of time ever made.

The first 100 years of Judo is a great and very historical DVD to own for just it's rare footage of Judo. The explaination and breakdown of the history of Judo is very interesting and gives you more of an understanding of this art.
